contentrichtext.text: '''[[Roger Moore]]''' (born 1927) is an English actor, most famous for his role as James Bond. '''Roger Moore''' may also refer to: * [[Roger Moore (computer scientist)]], designer and implementer of APL\360 * [[Roger Moore (poker player)]] (1938–2011), member of the Poker Hall of Fame * [[Roger E. Moore]] (born 1955), writer of roleplaying games including ''Dungeons & Dragons'' * [[Rory O'Moore (Irish noble)]] (c. 1600 – 1655), also known as Sir Roger Moore, a leader of the Irish Rebellion of 1641 == See also == *[[Roger More (disambiguation)]] * [[Moore (disambiguation)]] {{Hndis|name=Moore, Roger}}
